# Hyperbrowser App Examples

This map summarizes repository structure and important exploration paths. Start with subsystem nodes and follow evidence-backed links to inspect source files.

## Domain Clusters
- Explore [[idea-generator-reddit-app]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.
- Explore [[yc-research-bot-app]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.
- Explore [[competitor-tracker-data]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.

- Explore [[deep-crawler-bot-public]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.
- Explore [[hb-job-matcher-app]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.
- Explore [[scrape-to-api-app]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.
- Explore [[site-to-dataset-components]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.
- Explore [[web-to-agent-app]] to inspect related module behavior and evidence anchors.

## Explorations Needed
- Which subsystems should be prioritized for onboarding documentation?
- Which dependencies are high-risk and need version guardrails?
- Where should integration tests be expanded based on current topology?
